---

---

<section class="relative flex h-svh items-end overflow-hidden bg-wevol-black" data-hero>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <video
      class="hidden size-full object-cover md:block"
      src="videos/hero-desktop.webm"
      poster="images/hero-placeholder.webp"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      data-hero-video="desktop"
    ></video>
    <video
      class="size-full object-cover md:hidden"
      src="videos/hero-mobile.webm"
      poster="images/hero-placeholder-mobile.webp"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      data-hero-video="mobile"
    ></video>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(0deg, rgb(9, 9, 9) 0%, rgba(17, 17, 17, 0) 56.348%), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 100%);"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wv-container relative pb-[72px] pt-40 lg:pb-[92px] xl:pb-[112px]">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 text-center text-wevol-off-white xl:max-w-[1065px] xl:items-start xl:text-left">
      <h1
        class="wv-title text-5xl leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] md:text-7xl lg:max-w-[827px] lg:text-[96px] xl:max-w-[800px] 2xl:max-w-[1045px] 2xl:text-[128px]"
        data-reveal="words"
      >
        Evolução da saúde e performance
      </h1>
      <p
        class="wv-title-alt wv-ftype [--fs-min:24] [--fs-max:30] max-w-[800px] leading-[1.25]"
        data-reveal="lines"
      >
        Muito mais do que um treino. A WEVOL integra tecnologia, inteligência e acompanhamento
        personalizado para criar uma experiência única de evolução humana.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
